SMPP 3.4 PDU Packer/Unpacker Library.
This library is based partly on smpp34pdu (erlang/github) and JSMPP.

I am contributing to the smpp34pdu so I guess this project might help me
hone my skills in scala.

Implemented PDUs
	Packing
		BindTransmitter
	Unpacking
		BindTransmitter

TODO
	Packing
		A lot
	Unpacking
		BindTransmitter

Building
======================================
scoop uses sbt and an sbt/idea plugin. After you pull scoop, run 
	sbt update
	sbt idea
sbt can be downloaded from google(sbt)

Tests
====================================
	sbt test
